 (123,2,'红萌网能给你带来什么呢？','<h2><span style=\"font-family:\"黑体\";font-size:16pt;font-weight:bold;\">你想通过互联网改变你的生活吗？</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\"黑体\";font-size:16pt;font-weight:bold;\">你想拥有自己的网站吗？</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\"黑体\";font-size:16pt;font-weight:bold;\">你想通过网站赚美金吗？</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\"宋体\";font-size:10.5pt;\">红萌网是一家专业提供</span><span style=\"font-family:\"宋体\";font-size:10.5pt;\">IT<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">培训的网站，我们将市面上昂贵的培课程用最低的成本奉献给最需要的人</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\"宋体\";font-size:10.5pt;\">，帮助那些没有经济实力又渴望知识的有志者成就梦想，详情请查看</span><span><a href=\"http://www.redwww.com\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-family:\"宋体\";font-size:10.5pt;text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"15\">红萌网详细简介</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><br />\r\n<span><a href=\"http://www.redwww.com\"></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\"宋体\";font-size:10.5pt;\">为了使更多的有志者获益，红萌网推出<span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\">CPA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统，每个注册成为红萌网会员的朋友，都会获得一个推荐码，只要别人通过你的推荐码注册成为红萌网会员，并加入红萌网&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\">VIP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">你就会获得红萌网</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\">VIP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">价格</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\">10%(vip&nbsp;30%)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的拥金，你的帐上满</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元就可以兑现。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\