an><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">目录文件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">内核组织文件系统的基本节点</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">可以包含下一级目录文件或普通文件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">将所有内容组成一表</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">目录内文件名的列表</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">设备文件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">代表系统中的设备，在<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">/dev</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目录中</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">链接文件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">管道文件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">主要用于不同进程&nbsp;间的信息传递</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4.3Linux<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件结构</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">无论文件是一个程序、文档、数据库或目录，操作系统都会赋予它相同的结构：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">索引节点：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">又称<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">i</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节点，在文件系统中包含有关文件的信息的一个记录，包含文件权限、属主、大小、位置、日期等。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">数据：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">文件的实际内容，它可以是空的，也可以非常大，并且有自己的结构。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">文件名</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">尽量简单</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">最长可多达<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">255</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个字符</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">区分大小写</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4.4Linux<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目录结构</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">Linux<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统以文件目录的方式来组织和管理系统中的所有文件</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">Linux<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将所有文件及目录组织为一棵</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">倒挂</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的树</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">Filesystem&nbsp;Hierarchy&nbsp;Standard(FHS)</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件系统</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">操作系统对一个存储设备上的数据和元数据进行组织管理的机制</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">指文件存在的物理空间（文件的容器）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">Linux<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统中每个分区都是一个文件系统，都有自己的目录层次结构。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会将这些分属不同分区的、单独的文件系统按一定的方式形成一个系统总的目录层次结构。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4.6<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件系统的组成</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">一个文件系统是由逻辑块的序列组成的，每块为<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">512</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个字节。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">引导块：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;文件系统开始通常有一个扇区存放着启动操作系统的程序，每个文件系统都有一个引导块。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">超级块：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;记录文件系统的当前状态，如硬盘空间大小和文件系统的基本信息。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">索引节点：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;存放文件系统的索引节点表，<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统中每个文件和目录都占据一个索引节点。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">数据区：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;存放着文件数据</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4.7<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">常见的文件系统</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ext/ext2/ext3</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">JFS</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ReiserFS</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;m