\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-n&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后接要显行的行数</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">head&nbsp;-n&nbsp;20&nbsp;/etc/man.config</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">tail&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">取出文件后几行</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-n&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后接要显行的行数</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">tail&nbsp;-n&nbsp;20&nbsp;/etc/man.config</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">touch&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">修改文件时间或创建新文件</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-a<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--time=atime</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--time=access</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--time=use&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">只更改存取时间。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-c<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--no-create&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　不建立任何文件。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-d&lt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时间日期</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　使用指定的日期时间，而非现在的时间。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-m<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--time=mtime</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--time=modify&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　只更改变动时间。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">lab:</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">touch&nbsp;test1</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ls&nbsp;-l&nbsp;test1</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">cp&nbsp;-a&nbsp;~/.bashrc&nbsp;bashrc</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ll&nbsp;bashrc;ll&nbsp;--time=atime&nbsp;bashrc;&nbsp;ll&nbsp;--time&nbsp;=ctime&nbsp;bashrc</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">文件时间</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">mtime&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">内容数据修改时会改此时间</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ctime&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">状态改变会改此时间（权限与属性）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">atime&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">只是读取了文件，此时间就会改</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ls&nbsp;-l&nbsp;/etc/man.config</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ls&nbsp;-l&nbsp;--time=atime&nbsp;/etc/man.config</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ls&nbsp;-l&nbsp;--time=ctime&nbsp;/etc/man.config</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">高清视频下载</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<a class=\"redDown\" href=\"http://115.com/file/dn6d45id#&#13;&#10;7_文件和目录操作_03.zip\" target=\"_blank\">下载：7_文件和目录操作_03.zip</a>','',0,'','linux 红萌网','2011-04-08 16:52:53','这一节开始我们学习linux文件系统，包括文件系统、文件组成、文件和目录的相关操作等');
INSERT INTO `chapter` (`id`,`course_id`,`title`,`content`,`content_pic`,`is_free`,`vod_path`,`keywords`,`dates`,`abstracts`) VALUES 
 (37,2,'文件和目录操作_04','<p align=\"center\"><embed src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMjU2OTMzNzIw/v.swf\" quality=\"high\" width=\"606\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" allowscriptaccess=\"sameDomain\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><embed height=\"490\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"650\" src=\"http://www.docin.com/DocinViewer-173709252-144.swf\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">5.4<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件内容查阅</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">cat&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-n&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--number&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">由&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开始对所有输出的行数编号</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-b&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--number-nonblank&